s=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n唔可以平訓已經係痴線<br />\n<br />\n短個D我都會選擇經濟位，因為國泰D ON9機短途個D區域商務只係好少少既特選經濟，同普通經濟分別又唔係真係太大唔值得比咁貴去坐<br />\n<br />\n但長途真係差好遠..."},{"pid":"b86abf1a23ce46de39895f334628c7969ef8c064","tid":33044,"uid":88,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未坐過 覺得一樣<br />\n坐過就返唔到轉頭</blockquote><br />\n又唔係返唔到轉頭既<br />\n但的確商務爽好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n短程ok 既<br />\n長就一定要business"},{"pid":"403a4c292901bef37b8da5864f823ea43fcadebc","tid":33044,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:38:33.000Z","msg":"扮晒野"},{"pid":"d1551dad63492c4ca5349164ac4167ef4062a9f2","tid":33044,"uid":61728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:38:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好理班窮撚喇</blockquote><br />\n我就係冇依種心態，唔甘心佢地覺得我串...<br />\n經濟位最高級別個種唔係真係平商務太多<br />\n有時都會有d人為左彈性坐個種<br />\n<br />\n而如果夾到時間，我都會買最平個隻飛尤其係飛短途<br />\n錢唔係亂洗...亦唔係坐咩class代表你係咩人<br />\n<br />\n但佢地就當正我係特登扮野坐商務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bffcf2dc2eae5dac9c387fa2d77385ddf37cd78","tid":33044,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:39:29.000Z","msg":"咁似名校secret 啲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a283b5f651a33b3cd293e40422f921dd2f237d9","tid":33044,"uid":88,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:41:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要我坐10幾個鐘經濟我真係想像唔到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n唔可以平訓已經係痴線<br />\n<br />\n短個D我都會選擇經濟位，因為國泰D ON9機短途個D區域商務只係好少少既特選經濟，同普通經濟分別又唔係真係太大唔值得比咁貴去坐<br />\n<br />\n但長途真係差好遠...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上落唔洗等<br />\n拎gip 唔洗等<br />\n機艙可以黑媽媽<br />\n出出入入 唔洗要人讓<br />\n去toilet 唔洗迫<br />\n野食又正<br />\n平訓打直做運動 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6ad78aa8a314c0fbd1863243219c51bd057c5d","tid":33044,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:44:11.000Z","msg":"成世未坐過商務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係想像唔到坐商務係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申一年大概飛8-10次都係坐私人飛機"},{"pid":"18611e5cfbd7741611dc1e7daa01ebf297c6c89d","tid":33044,"uid":20061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:45:00.000Z","msg":"我轉機去英國20個鐘都係經濟位<br />\n其實冇咩問題 唔想洗咁多錢咪坐經濟位<br />\n你又唔洗講到好似會死咁既<br />\n不過中意坐邊願意花錢都冇問題<br />\n人地唔抵得你姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148121de96ca9fd5ad110d3fd75af025df522b34","tid":33044,"uid":34987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:45:35.000Z","msg":"講真去到歐洲 一陣你班同學又要懶係咩體驗要窮遊訓街 你要住酒店 大家目標唔一樣最後都係搵黎搞<br />\n利申. 支持坐商務"},{"pid":"275955f3165d593ca04381f3446f12d4607b2853","tid":33044,"uid":61728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:45:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要我坐10幾個鐘經濟我真係想像唔到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n唔可以平訓已經係痴線<br />\n<br />\n短個D我都會選擇經濟位，因為國泰D ON9機短途個D區域商務只係好少少既特選經濟，同普通經濟分別又唔係真係太大唔值得比咁貴去坐<br />\n<br />\n但長途真係差好遠...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上落唔洗等<br />\n拎gip 唔洗等<br />\n機艙可以黑媽媽<br />\n出出入入 唔洗要人讓<br />\n去toilet 唔洗迫<br />\n野食又正<br />\n平訓打直做運動 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過其實洗唔洗等人出分別唔大<br />\n尤其香港機場出行李慢到痴，你最早落同最遲落一樣係要等行李<br />\n不過有得拎行李先係真係方便既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其餘既坐短程真係感受唔到，所以真係唔多坐商務...<br />\n野食的話，商務位都好短程機大把人唔食/只係食某部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以唔洗話特別好"},{"pid":"a86864ec814fa4644a14c16469ff4c5a93e68f2e","tid":33044,"uid":9188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:48:44.000Z","msg":"如果佢地連你坐business都要話你<br />\n咁其實你成個trip都唔洗玩<br />\n一定仲多唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 試過, 依家免得過都唔會同fd去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c3a2b788f9abdb7a3668bddddd02be691d1078","tid":33044,"uid":15659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:02:26.000Z","msg":"何必要同窮撚做朋友？"},{"pid":"5a3eb7755848d13616d554069430498bdf0f17ef","tid":33044,"uid":6420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"國泰學生飛要到上之前48個鐘先揀得位<br />\n有機會可以一齊坐既<br />\n不過你有錢就梗係坐商務舒服好多啦"},{"pid":"a4d2f8c11a770c3c6647324bbe3d8030ee39473d","tid":33044,"uid":20622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:12:15.000Z","msg":"好心坐first class la<br />\n坐商務窄點坐十幾個鐘"},{"pid":"9bc2a6d4da44d63a7d4eb8d7d5545cd11a8b194c","tid":33044,"uid":45407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:14:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4557eddd4